name: Create a Brand Strategy with ChatGPT and Google Sheets
description:
Combine the analytical power of ChatGPT with the versatility of Google Sheets to create a data-driven brand strategy. This approach helps you analyze trends and make informed decisions quickly.

Estimated number of ChatGPT tokens used by this template: 4,000 tokens for prompts and 1,000 tokens for a completion.

[What are tokens and how to count them?](https://help.openai.com/en/articles/4936856-what-are-tokens-and-how-to-count-them)
